Name: Task Force 88: Hostile Contact
About the game: Features Six exciting game play modes: Deathmatch, Team Deathmatch, Conquest, Rush, Capture the Flag, and Kill Confirmed. Four world-wide exotic battle locations. Different player classes are available; Assault, Support, Medic and Recon each with a special skill set. All perks and weapons issued immediately, just like the real military. No need for tiresome grinding. Select your gear and skill set. Now fight your way to glory! Play as single player with AI bots, or multiplayer, online or LAN. Choose First or Third Person perspective. Engage your opponents in either close quarter combat or long-distance battles. Communicate with others via in-game text and global proximity voice chat.
